{"tid":1525463,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今日起，搞黨鐵的鐵路部份都係鬼，好多人靠黨鐡走，黨鐵有好多商場","createTime":"2019-09-01T00:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T12:05:03.000Z","uid":273188,"like":21,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ef01583fb8ed43afc10a66e0af1943bd2a369454","tid":1525463,"uid":273188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T00:36:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全面罷買黨鐵商場</span></span><br />\n港鐵商場 (<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;替代商場</span></span>)<br />\n圓方<br />\n德福廣場(<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;淘大花園/商場</span></span>)<br />\n青衣城  (<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">改去---&gt;青怡廣場</span></span>)<br />\nPopCorn (<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;將軍澳廣場</span></span>)<br />\n綠楊坊 (<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">改去---&gt;荃灣千色滙</span></span>)<br />\nCitylink 連城廣場(<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">改去---&gt;沙田中心</span></span>)<br />\n杏花新城<br />\n連理街 (<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;將軍澳廣場</span></span>)<br />\n海趣坊 (<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;啟豐商場</span></span></span>)<br />\n駿景廣場 (<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;銀禧花園</span></span></span>)<br />\n新屯門商場 (<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">改去---&gt;富健花園</span></span>)<br />\n恒福商場 (<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">改去---&gt;置樂商場</span></span>)<br />\nThe lohas(<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;將軍澳廣場</span></span>)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/shops/more_malls.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fshops%2Fmore_malls.html&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=9e32084f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/shops/more_malls.html</a>"},{"pid":"145a4fe9633670d6f66b595d3a87fee67cdea5d9","tid":1525463,"uid":141070,"like":5,"dislike":25,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T00:38:08.000Z","msg":"搞鐵根本係自取滅亡<br />\n車站重兵"},{"pid":"da99802b267bd61230046c6fe9d197b82c13d99f","tid":1525463,"uid":40001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c59764ab8afcd99a346783294b870fc4cb9ec68d","tid":1525463,"uid":162499,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T00:42:12.000Z","msg":"1,罷搭港鐵行動,呢個係最簡單直接既做法(當然你都可以選擇跳閘),改為搭巴士,踩單車,坐渡海小輪甚至行路去返工之類<br />\nQ1:點解冇小巴同的士?<br />\nA1:小巴既話,你唔好忘記上次佔中潮聯單野,的士既話,班愛國的士唔係好明顯啦咩?<br />\n<br />\n2,罷搭港鐵升級版:向其他人(包括遊客),宣傳港鐵過去做過既行動,邀請佢地加入罷搭行動,即使佢地拒絕參與行動,都唔洗惡這相向,我地可以好熱心咁問佢地目的地係邊,然後向佢地推薦去果度既其他方法(推薦其他巴士路線,或者教佢裝九巴,城巴APP之類),記住,呢個係任何地點,任何社交網絡都可以宣傳到<br />\n<br />\n3,罷買港鐵沿線商店及附屬港鐵商場,簡單D黎講,就係拒絕消費,令有關店舖收入大減,若港鐵不減租,店舖必然虧損,自然無法長期經營,最終停止業務,若港鐵減租,則租金收入大減,呢個行動雖然會濫炒到商戶,尤其是港鐵企硬唔減租既話,但係冇辦法,呢個一定要濫炒埋佢<br />\n<br />\n4,抵制地鐵廣告客戶,逼使向港鐵提出終止廣告業務,呢個做法同上次抵制向CCTVB黃金時段落廣告一樣,所以我唔再重複<br />\n<br />\n呢4個行動,係我暫時諗到係香港人可以即時做到既野,記住,呢個係長期戰爭,係唔可能1日就成功"},{"pid":"eca1c6406982397c533cd00fdd5c1246f6ba30bd","tid":1525463,"uid":202464,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T00:44:02.000Z","msg":"點解你既思維係二選一？"},{"pid":"61d35bf3f84cbdd30805d1736039ef8593662384","tid":1525463,"uid":120627,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T00:50:57.000Z","msg":"黨鐵同黑警合作<br />\n點走啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac34419782a629ff7bc0609c34134bae80919877","tid":1525463,"uid":147416,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T00:52:50.000Z","msg":"破壞完，so what. 整番唔多＄，有vdeo拉多一個義士。<br />\n<br />\n轉買etc 有用D，尤其不要買7丶華結！"},{"pid":"e51086d6c209e45bd075396e5be